        <mxCell id="ssdONVnJytb1tMgbgSI7-37" value="Responsible for detecting when the DOM API has made an error.&lt;div&gt;Finds discrepencies in the given resume and the form that has been filled.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Records passes and failures.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Failures cause a re-generation and update of the indexed DOM API implementation.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;After re-generation, the API is used and verified again to see if it passes.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;If it fails again after re-generation, it gets put on human operator intervention queue for further investigation.&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;resizable=0;points=[];autosize=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;" vertex="1" parent="1">
